---
title: G Jewelry
layout: "base.njk"
---

<div id="about" class="container py-6">
  <div class="columns is-centered">
    <div class="column is-two-thirds has-text-centered">
      <h1 class="title is-2">About Grayson Caroll</h1>
      <p class="subtitle is-5 has-text-grey mt-3">
        Second-generation local jeweler dedicated to craftsmanship and quality.
      </p>
      <p class="content is-medium mt-5">
        Grayson Caroll grew up in his father's workshop, where he developed a deep appreciation for the art of creating timeless jewelry. His work combines traditional techniques with modern design, resulting in pieces that are both unique and elegant.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="gallery" class="container py-6 has-background-darker-grey">
  <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered">Our Work</h1>
  <div class="columns is-multiline mt-5">
    {% for item in collections.gallery %}
      <div class="column is-one-third">
        <div class="card is-fullheight">
          <a class="card-image" data-modal-target="image-modal" href="#">
            <figure class="image is-4by3">
              <img src="{{ item.data.image }}" alt="{{ item.data.alt }}">
            </figure>
          </a>

        </div>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

<div id="image-modal" class="modal">
  <div class="modal-background"></div>
  <div class="modal-content">
    <p class="image">
      <img src="#" alt="">
    </p>
  </div>
  <button class="modal-close is-large" aria-label="close"></button>
</div>

<div id="contact" class="container py-6">
  <div class="columns is-centered">
    <div class="column is-two-thirds">
      <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered">Contact Us</h1>
      <form netlify class="box mt-5">
        <div class="field">
          <label class="label">Name</label>
          <div class="control">
            <input class="input" type="text" placeholder="Your Name" name="name" required>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label class="label">Email</label>
          <div class="control">
            <input class="input" type="email" placeholder="Your Email" name="email" required>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label class="label">Message</label>
          <div class="control">
            <textarea class="textarea" placeholder="Your Message" name="message" required></textarea>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field is-grouped is-justify-content-flex-end">
          <div class="control">
            <button class="button is-link" type="submit">Send Message</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
